Package data_managers

Class CineplexManager

java.lang.Object
data_managers.CineplexManager
public class CineplexManager extends Object
The CineplexManager class takes care of interacting with the file where the cineplexes are stored. It performs writing, updating, reading and searching in the cineplexes' storage.
